easy.name: Easy
easy.explanation: An easy difficulty recommended for people new to action games.

normal.name: Normal
normal.explanation: Recommended for people who want to enjoy Yakuza 6 normally.

hard.name: Hard
hard.explanation: A harder difficulty for people who are skilled at playing action games.

legend.name: Legend
legend.explanation:
The toughest difficulty for anyone who wishes to master Yakuza 6 to
its fullest.

free_camera_vertical.name: Camera Control (Vertical)
free_camera_vertical.explanation: Change how to move the camera vertically.

free_camera_horizontal.name: Camera Control (Horizontal)
free_camera_horizontal.explanation: Change how to move the camera horizontally.

brightness.name: Brightness
brightness.explanation: Slide the cursor to adjust the brightness.

gamma.name: Gamma
gamma.explanation: Slide the cursor to adjust the gamma correction.

camera_sensitivity.name: Camera Movement Speed
camera_sensitivity.explanation:
Set the speed the camera moves at. 
Slide the cursor to adjust the speed.

pov_camera_vertical.name: First-Person View (Vertical)
pov_camera_vertical.explanation: Change how to move the first-person camera vertically.

pov_camera_horizontal.name: First-Person View (Horizontal)
pov_camera_horizontal.explanation: Change how to move the first-person camera horizontally.

minimap_visible.name: Minimap Display
minimap_visible.explanation:
Switch on/off the minimap that appears in the lower
left part of the screen.

blood_type.name: Blood Level
blood_type.explanation: Set the level of blood to display.

font_kind.name: Set Font
font_kind.explanation: Change the font used during the game.

minimap_direction.name: Minimap Rotation
minimap_direction.explanation:
Switch on/off minimap rotation. If turned on,
the minimap will rotate with the camera.

subtitles_display.name: Subtitles
subtitles_display.explanation: Switch on/off subtitles for movie scenes.

speaker_type.name: Speaker Type
speaker_type.explanation: Select between stereo, surround 5.1 or surround 7.1 sound.

speaker_front_angle.name: Front
speaker_front_angle.explanation: Adjust to your speakers' angle for optimal quality.

speaker_rear_angle.name: Back
speaker_rear_angle.explanation: Adjust to your speakers' angle for optimal quality.

auto_camera.name: Auto Camera
auto_camera.explanation:
The camera's point of view will move automatically
depending on the situation. If you select Off, it
will not move unless the player moves it themselves.

hud_enabled.name: HUD Visible
hud_enabled.explanation: Toggle ingame HUD on or off.

graphics_output.name: Output Device
graphics_output.explanation: Select output device for given adapter.

graphics_display_mode.name: Display Mode
graphics_display_mode.explanation: Set display mode for your device.

graphics_display_resolution.name: Resolution
graphics_display_resolution.explanation: Set display resolution for your device.

graphics_refresh_rate.name: Refresh Rate
graphics_refresh_rate.explanation: Set refresh rate of your display device.

graphics_vertical_sync.name: Vertical Sync
graphics_vertical_sync.explanation: Set vertical synchronization for your display device.

graphics_quality_preset.name: Quality
graphics_quality_preset.explanation: Use presets to easily control advanced graphics settings.

graphics_ssao.name: SSAO
graphics_ssao.explanation: Enable or disable Screen Space Ambient Occlusion.

graphics_aa.name: Anti-aliasing
graphics_aa.explanation: Set anti-aliasing type or disable it.

graphics_dof.name: Depth of Field
graphics_dof.explanation: Enable or disable Depth of Field.

icon_select.name: Icon Select
icon_select.explanation: Option to choose what icons will be used.

disable_windows_key.name: Disable Windows Key
disable_windows_key.explanation: Disable Windows Key while the game is running.

tattoo_bars.name: Letterbox Artworks
tattoo_bars.explanation:
Enable or disable tattoo letterbox artwork
used in aspect ratios different than 16:9.

mouse_cursor.name: Mouse Cursor
mouse_cursor.explanation: Set mouse pointer to game or system style.

speaker_front_angle_7_1.name: Front
speaker_front_angle_7_1.explanation: Adjust to your speakers' angle for optimal quality.

speaker_surround_angle_5_1.name: Surround
speaker_surround_angle_5_1.explanation: Adjust to your speakers' angle for optimal quality.

speaker_surround_angle_7_1.name: Surround
speaker_surround_angle_7_1.explanation: Adjust to your speakers' angle for optimal quality.

speaker_rear_angle_7_1.name: Back
speaker_rear_angle_7_1.explanation: Adjust to your speakers' angle for optimal quality.

graphics_ui_limit_ui.name: UI Layout Width Limit
graphics_ui_limit_ui.explanation:
Set maximum aspect ratio for the layout of UI elements.
Can be used to shift UI from the edges toward the center 
of the screen.

graphics_ui_limit_minigame.name: Middle Screen View Limit
graphics_ui_limit_minigame.explanation:
Set aspect ratio of the middle display. Can be used to fit 
parts of the game entirely within the primary screen of 
the multi-monitor configuration.

hide_skip_prompt.name: Hide Skip prompt in dialogues
hide_skip_prompt.explanation:
Hides the Skip prompt in dialogues. 
Skipping dialogues is still possible.
